description: The number of cases of Chlymida and the rate per 100,000 people by select metropolitan statistical areas in the United States.  A value indicated by 0" means no data was available.  STD morbidity reporting methods do not allow MSA-specific case counts and rates to be determined for some jurisdictions for some years.
